line_1: Their eldest hope, their Jenny, worman-grown,
line_2: At Service out, amang the Farmers roun';

line_1: Their eldest hope, their Jenny, worman-grown,
line_2: A cannie errand to a neebor town:

line_1: Their eldest hope, their Jenny, worman-grown,
line_2: Comes hame, perhaps, to shew a braw new gown,
